                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 17.53,
                                "byte_start": 100549,
                                "byte_stop": 170766,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 76-444 and the consolidated case 76-454, Northeast Marine Terminal against Caputo and the related case will be announced by Mr. Justice Marshall."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 17.53,
                        "stop": 120.004,
                        "byte_start": 170766,
                        "byte_stop": 580575,
                        "speaker": {
                            "ID": 15104,
                            "name": "Thurgood Marshall",
                            "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/people\/thurgood_marshall",
                            "last_name": "Marshall",
                            "roles": [
                                {
                                    "id": 2748,
                                    "type": "scotus_justice",
                                    "date_start": -71002800,
                                    "date_end": 686293200,
                                    "appointing_president": "Lyndon B. Johnson",
                                    "role_title": "Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                                    "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/preson_role\/scotus_justice\/2748"
                                }
                            ],
                            "thumbnail": {
                                "id": 32770,
                                "mime": "image\/png",
                                "size": 59272,
                                "href": "https:\/\/api.oyez.org\/sites\/default\/files\/thurgood_marshall.png"
                            },
                            "length_of_service": 8765,
                            "identifier": "thurgood_marshall"
                        },
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 17.53,
                                "stop": 33.935,
                                "byte_start": 170766,
                                "byte_stop": 236386,
                                "text": "These consolidated cases here on writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit required that we determine the extent of coverage provided by the Federal Longshoremen\u0027s and Harbor Workers\u0027 Compensation Act."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 33.935,
                                "stop": 41.844,
                                "byte_start": 236386,
                                "byte_stop": 267942,
                                "text": "Prior to 1972, the Act covered only injuries that occurred on the navigable waters of the United States."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 41.844,
                                "stop": 52.723,
                                "byte_start": 267942,
                                "byte_stop": 311514,
                                "text": "Longshoremen\u0027s and Harbor Workers who were injured on the land were ineligible for federal compensation and had to rely exclusively on state compensation remedies."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 52.723,
                                "stop": 64.697,
                                "byte_start": 311514,
                                "byte_stop": 359370,
                                "text": "Using the water\u0027s edge as a line of demarcation, however, prove to be unsatisfactory for these amphibious occupations whose work is performed on both the ship and the shore."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 64.697,
                                "stop": 69.741,
                                "byte_start": 359370,
                                "byte_stop": 379537,
                                "text": "Accordingly in 1972, Congress changed the scope of the coverage."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 69.741,
                                "stop": 82.605,
                                "byte_start": 379537,
                                "byte_stop": 431050,
                                "text": "It retained the so-called \u0022situs test\u0022 which looks to the location of the injured, but it enlarged the coverage areas to include in addition to the water, piers, wharf and terminals."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 82.605,
                                "stop": 98.89,
                                "byte_start": 431050,
                                "byte_stop": 496147,
                                "text": "It also added a so-called \u0022status test\u0022 which require that the injured employee be engaged in maritime employment including as relevant to these cases longshoreman and other persons engaged in longshoring operations."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 98.89,
                                "stop": 110.774,
                                "byte_start": 496147,
                                "byte_stop": 543690,
                                "text": "At issue in these cases is whether respondents, Caputo and Blundo injured while working on the New York waterfront met these requirements of the amended Act."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 110.774,
                                "stop": 120.004,
                                "byte_start": 543690,
                                "byte_stop": 580575,
                                "text": "For the reasons stated and an opinion filed with the clerk today, we find that they did and affirmed the judgment."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
